Designer's notes
If the player attacks A-base and fails to kill Platonov, he (Platonov) uses teleport to hide in one of the other bases the player did not capture yet. This base becomes A-base for the purposes of dialogues - use A-BaseRefuse if Burlak comes close to it. If the player destroys this base a well, Platonov runs off the map.

If on the other hand the player ignores A-base, Platonov will construct a Behemoth and attack him.

